  "instructions": [
    "Thread the bamboo shoots, onion, carrot, and garlic onto skewers.",
    "In a large bowl, mix together the chopped parsley, cumin, coriander, paprika, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add the olive oil and lemon juice to the bowl and mix well.",
    "Preheat a grill or grill pan to medium-high heat.",
    "Brush the skewers with the olive oil mixture and grill for 10-12 minutes, turning occasionally.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy!"
